headline: WTW Announces Regular Quarterly Dividend
summary: LONDON, Feb. 24, 2025 (GLOBE NEWSWIRE) -- WTW (NASDAQ: WTW), a leading global advisory, broking and solutions company, announced that its Board of Directors approved a regular quarterly cash dividend of $0.92 per common share for the quarter ended December 31, 2024. This represents a 5% increase to the prior quarter’s dividend. The dividend is payable on or about April 15, 2025 to shareholders of record at the close of business on March 31, 2025.
